				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\Delta F \approx - \Delta C$$\end{document}ΔF≈-ΔC

Combining these decompositions with Eq. 1a gives:1b\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
